GA WDI NYC Jan 14, Project 1

Overview



Technologies Used

Ruby 2.1.0
Ruby on Rails 4.0.2
PostgreSQL Database
Authentication & Authorization from scratch using bcrypt-ruby
Google Place API
Google Maps API
Word Cloud Maker API
HTTParty

User Stories:
- As a user, I can find a location so that I can review/tag it
- As a user, I can check into place 
- As a user, i can tag a place when I check in
- As a user, I can browse places and see tags associated to places
- As a user, I can add a new place
- As a user, I can log in and out

Backlog

A full list of user stories can be found by looking at this Pivotal Tracker Project